#### 2.1 重新提取推特id[¶](#2.1-重新提取推特id)

In [8]:

```
twitter['id'] = twitter['url'].str.split('/').str[-1]
```

#### 2.2 处理时间[¶](#2.2-处理时间)

In [9]:

```
twitter['dmy'] = twitter['timestamp'].str.split(' ').str[0]
twitter['dmy'] = pd.to_datetime(twitter['dmy'],dayfirst=True,format="%d-%m-%Y")
```

In [10]:

```
#timestamp类型转换为时间类型
twitter['timestamp'] = pd.to_datetime(twitter['timestamp'],dayfirst=True)
```

In [11]:

```
#统计每月推特发送总数
twitter['year'] = twitter['timestamp'].dt.year
twitter['month'] = twitter['timestamp'].dt.month

twitter['time'] = twitter['timestamp'].dt.hour
```

#### 3.9 查看每条推特的平均点赞量[¶](#3.9-查看每条推特的平均点赞量)

In [27]:

```
df5 = twitter.groupby(['year','month']).id.count().reset_index(name='count_t')
df6 = (twitter.groupby(['year','month']).likes.sum()/10000).reset_index(name='likes')
df6['mean_t'] = df6['likes']/df5['count_t']
plt.figure(figsize=(8,6))
sns.lineplot(data=df6,x='month',y='mean_t',hue='year')
plt.title('平均每条推特的点赞量',loc='left',fontsize=14)
plt.xlabel('month',fontsize=12)
plt.ylabel('点 赞   (万次)',fontsize=12)
plt.show()
```

```
import nltk
from wordcloud import WordCloud,STOPWORDS
from subprocess import check_output
from nltk.corpus import stopwords
stopwords_set = set(stopwords.words('english'))
```

In [31]:

```
text = twitter['tweet']

def wordcloud_draw(data,color = 'white'):
    words =''.join(data)
    cleaned_word = " ".join([word for word in words.split()
                            if 'https' not in word
                             and len(word)>=3
                                and not word.startswith('@')
                                and not word.startswith('#')
                                and word != 'co'
                            ])
    wordcloud = WordCloud(stopwords=stopwords_set,
                          background_color=color,
                          width=2500,
                          height=2000).generate(cleaned_word)
    plt.figure(1,figsize =(13,13))
    plt.imshow(wordcloud)
    plt.axis('off')
    plt.show()

wordcloud_draw(text)
```
